  <brief_title>Electrophysiologic Parameters and Biomarkers Predicting Treatment Response in Patients With Major Depressive Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study of Escitalopram Treatment and Biomarkers in Major Depressive Disorder</official_title>
